{
    "scenario_name": "10_ecommerce_platform",
    "description": "Large-scale e-commerce platform with 40 hosts and a 5-level dependency chain: web tier (web_cdn + 3 web frontends + 2 load balancers), API tier (2 gateways + auth x2 + catalog x2 + order x2 + payment + notification + search + recommendation + review + image), data tier (user_db master+slave, catalog_db master+slave, orders_db, payment_db x2, search_index, session_cache x2, analytics_db), infrastructure (message_queue x2 + cdn_origin + admin_console + backup + monitoring + log_aggregator + kibana_dashboard + reporting). Exercises all 7 hardening actions with 3 reuse_service cases, 2 turnoff_safely cases, 3 patch_with_attention cases, 3 patch_service cases and a broad mix of migrate_service and disable_service.",
